OL,3,C70-mile diversion to end after
OL,4,Croadworks in Powys
OL,6,FThe Cabinet Secretary for Transport
OL,7,Fand North Wales, Ken Skates has
OL,8,Fconfirmed that the A470 between
OL,9,FTalerddig and Dolfach will reopen as
OL,10,Fplanned on 11 April with traffic
OL,11,Fmanagement in place.
OL,13,FThe works involving complex and
OL,14,Fextensive repairs to the retaining
OL,15,Fwall above the adjacent Afon Laen
OL,16,Finvolved the full closure of the road
OL,17,Fbetween 20 January and 11 April.2-way
OL,18,Ftraffic lights will now be reinstalled
OL,19,Fat the site whilst a safety barrier is
OL,20,Finstalled.
