OL,3,C70-mile diversion to end after
OL,4,Croadworks in Powys
OL,6,FAll traffic management will be removed
OL,7,Ffrom the site by 30 April 2025. Every
OL,8,Feffort will be made to reduce this
OL,9,Ftimeframe if possible. The work
OL,10,Fprovides a permanent solution on this
OL,11,Fstretch of road which has had traffic
OL,12,Fmanagement in place since an emergency
OL,13,Fclosure in October 2023, when a
OL,14,Fretaining wall which supported the
OL,15,Froad partially collapsed.
