OL,3,C70-mile diversion to end after
OL,4,Croadworks in Powys
OL,6,FKen Skates said,"I understand the
OL,7,Fdisruption caused by the works and I'd
OL,8,Flike to thank motorists and local
OL,9,Fresidents for their patience whilst
OL,10,Fthe work was taking place. However, it
OL,11,Fwas vital this work was carried out at
OL,12,Fthis time to ensure the road can
OL,13,Fremain open in the years to come."
OL,15,F"I'd also like to thank the North and
OL,16,FMid Wales Trunk Road Agent and their
OL,17,Fsupply chain for their hard work to
OL,18,Fensure the work was completed on
OL,19,Fschedule whilst minimising disruption
OL,20,Fas far as possible."
